description.value: This value set represents values associated with pregnancy conditions diagnoses, outcomes, and state.

purpose.value: The purpose of this value set is to define pregnancy conditions diagnoses, outcomes, and states.

copyright.value: Please see NLM VSAC (https://vsac.nlm.nih.gov/) for the latest version of the value sets: Pregnancy 2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.378, Complications of Pregnancy, Childbirth and the Puerperium 2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.111.12.1012, and Complications of Pregnancy, Childbirth and the Puerperium (ICD 9) 2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.111.11.1021.
